{"layout":"logicalStructure","root":{"data":{"text":"<p>MyBatis 动态 sql有什么用?执行原理?有哪些动态 sql?</p>","expand":true,"uid":"2e3065d1-3040-4cd9-85fa-5757925942d9","richText":true,"isActive":false,"imgMap":{}},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p>动态sql有什么用</p>","uid":"6989749b-b0f9-4000-8a3a-8fd38284155c","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p>动态SQL是在MyBatis中根据不同的条件、需求动态生成 sQL语句的一种机制。它的主要目的是提高SQL的灵活性和复用性,在复杂的查询或更新场景中,根据参数动态构建不同的SQL语句。</p>","uid":"e673f740-8e15-4187-82df-eaf99c23de3a","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"<p>执行原理</p>","uid":"5bea2e92-591a-4c87-b752-cf07d428c916","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p>动态SQL的执行以XML映射文件中定义的SQL片段及特定标签为依赖基础，其核心包含if、choose、when、otherwise、where、foreach等标签，执行时先对这些标签进行解析，再在运行过程中依据传入的参数值进行评估判断，最终生成完整的SQL语句并发送至数据库完成执行。</p>","uid":"d402fafa-93dd-4a01-8a5f-80973220414e","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false,"note":"### MyBatis解析动态SQL的流程\nMyBatis解析动态SQL主要有以下流程：\n- **解析动态SQL**：在映射文件加载时，MyBatis会解析XML文件中的动态SQL标签。\n- **参数绑定**：当执行SQL语句时，MyBatis会根据传入的参数绑定具体的值。\n- **生成最终SQL**：根据参数值和动态SQL标签生成最终的SQL语句。\n- **执行SQL**：MyBatis执行生成的SQL语句，并返回结果。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"text":"<p>有哪些动态 sql</p>","uid":"229a6044-1021-4044-a642-098786c392c7","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[{"data":{"text":"<p>if、choose、when、otherwise、where、foreach</p>","uid":"bd64ccef-9ca3-42b2-b764-8b066306e625","expand":true,"richText":true,"isActive":false},"children":[]}]}],"smmVersion":"0.14.0-fix.1"},"theme":{"template":"classic4","config":{}},"view":{"transform":{"scaleX":1,"scaleY":1,"shear":0,"rotate":0,"translateX":-763,"translateY":-51,"originX":0,"originY":0,"a":1,"b":0,"c":0,"d":1,"e":-763,"f":-51},"state":{"scale":1,"x":-763,"y":-51,"sx":-734,"sy":-53}}}